      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; nominal input values sourced from experimental dataset with documented provenance.",
      "rationale": "Model input uncertainty (fluid properties, geometry tolerances) was not formally propagated at MRL 2. All input values were sourced directly from the FDA benchmark experimental dataset with full documentation. Sensitivity of RH to ±5% variation in viscosity was checked informally and found to produce < 3% change in predicted RH, providing adequate informal confidence. Gradation 1 is accepted."
    },
